{"tid":354464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位請幫幫我媽媽","createTime":"2017-08-10T13:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T07:59:30.000Z","uid":18800,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dec3d1fc44e97561478e613b3c8e7af2e163078","tid":354464,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:11:19.000Z","msg":"我媽有網球手, 睇左幾間唔同既西醫, 但都係開d消炎止痛藥, 一停食就痛返, 咁我媽媽就轉睇中醫針灸, 但睇左六千幾蚊(分十次睇)都好仲係痛, 個中醫話比d時間慢慢黎(明朋我媽15年嗰時都係網球手去同一間中醫睇都睇得好)<br />\n<br />\n連埋之前睇既西醫, 又打針又食藥, 加加埋埋藥費真係好貴, 大家有冇親戚朋友試過網球手睇得好架??"},{"pid":"2679d214f42d3c358da43b458d6dc13de626b0e4","tid":354464,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:14:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"833800d5138a1447baa609a814cc3841862ddc38","tid":354464,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe04b1ff8f7cec14dc0bd46890a78ae961544f62","tid":354464,"uid":46566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"試下去沙灘游水"},{"pid":"5a11c20320825836c39e4ef932aade812f077ef8","tid":354464,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:21:33.000Z","msg":"你媽咩原因網球手？"},{"pid":"e57f8f7b9697416d6f06411f0b8112f6f3721d59","tid":354464,"uid":37853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:23:43.000Z","msg":"你都要講佢做咩有網球手ga <br />\n工作關係定點先<br />\n有無照過X-ray 或者 mri 睇下有無骨刺呀？"},{"pid":"a4a8f431618fe44d44d582f31d7e308020d1dbc0","tid":354464,"uid":122331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:25:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"845874ec57ec28766e3b032fff8bf0c6a97f3cd5","tid":354464,"uid":8786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:26:17.000Z","msg":"睇中醫十次都冇好係咪應該諗下搵個有料既醫？"},{"pid":"f58e218c680f29df797e88f2d1914557dfa69e4d","tid":354464,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"醫生話做嘢勞損引致, 我媽份工都要體力勞動<br />\n但份工好難請假, 遲職唔做又搵唔到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67065d63df752e0131ca8978247aead75399a8c","tid":354464,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇中醫十次都冇好係咪應該諗下搵個有料既醫？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為佢兩年前試過喺呢間中醫睇好左, 所以先去返呢間睇<br />\n至於你話點解睇十次係因為我媽join左個療程, 抵d, 同埋個中醫成日話慢慢黎......要d時間先會好返"},{"pid":"fda95bb13dbca99479c7d092617c12a946bb42dc","tid":354464,"uid":131512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"買個護腕俾媽媽？"},{"pid":"ccd7b0a6d839e404bad3eda7c4831abe46eee698","tid":354464,"uid":90231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:32:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/E7sWpDKsF_g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE7sWpDKsF_g&d=EFZLmz7Nm0vHz0x7LOGjWTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4bee776c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E7sWpDKsF_g</a><br />\n<br />\n試下做呢個運動<br />\n要慢慢控制住個重物落去，落個下緊要過上，上可以用第二隻手協助，每次做十下左右，休息一分鐘後再做，一日做三次十下，揀個重量係只會有少少痛，做完幾個鐘後亦唔可以覺得好痛<br />\n<br />\n初初做個時會有少少痛，慢慢會做到無痛，無痛之後再加重個重量，不斷加不斷加<br />\n<br />\n網球手係慢性筋腱炎症，除左做運動既時間要儘量休息，feel到紅腫熱時可以冰敷15分鐘減輕症狀，otw可以熱敷20分鐘，但要小心燒傷<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你"},{"pid":"2ede2cfdc986809a9cadf821385bb42c947248a1","tid":354464,"uid":35313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"試下去石硤尾睇友琛堂"},{"pid":"d7201262ddf3b142810a86c4402b68aaaa546aea","tid":354464,"uid":133750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:32:45.000Z","msg":"應該係繼續做粗重野都好難完全好返"},{"pid":"6fb3251587c737bae8b32cb40163101d641af672","tid":354464,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/E7sWpDKsF_g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE7sWpDKsF_g&d=EFZLmz7Nm0vHz0x7LOGjWTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4bee776c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E7sWpDKsF_g</a><br />\n<br />\n試下做呢個運動<br />\n要慢慢控制住個重物落去，落個下緊要過上，上可以用第二隻手協助，每次做十下左右，休息一分鐘後再做，一日做三次十下，揀個重量係只會有少少痛，做完幾個鐘後亦唔可以覺得好痛<br />\n<br />\n初初做個時會有少少痛，慢慢會做到無痛，無痛之後再加重個重量，不斷加不斷加<br />\n<br />\n網球手係慢性筋腱炎症，除左做運動既時間要儘量休息，feel到紅腫熱時可以冰敷15分鐘減輕症狀，otw可以熱敷20分鐘，但要小心燒傷<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好有心, 唔該曬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26b6539570dc559f0bbbf66abb7f6153ed73356","tid":354464,"uid":135208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T13:34:59.000Z","msg":"試下睇荃灣黃振球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e6a606d5454f749352caed5e2574113afe350f","tid":354464,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T14:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a550840755fefba9d79851d3fee5b70b14ddded","tid":354464,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c7e6e630bceb12ab49690bf3846b1ebd65810c","tid":354464,"uid":93642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T01:18:40.000Z","msg":"牛頭角何兆萬"},{"pid":"e25e661c14d29c536dc5fb2fd82bba18376d6c78","tid":354464,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴打"},{"pid":"4619868190d419371513269e99a962e509b6a1fe","tid":354464,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:08:29.000Z","msg":"油麻地林上立"},{"pid":"67cec509c75ca722af02f6a39905f19def7f8510","tid":354464,"uid":93642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"天水圍劉馬車"},{"pid":"22b1744f138629c76f28694c666c7e49c5c34c85","tid":354464,"uid":72093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-1